import React from 'react'
import {Routes, Route} from 'react-router-dom'
import Auth from '../components/Auth'

const RouteViews = (props) => (<main>
    <Routes>
        <Route path="/login" render={() => <Auth authType = "login"/>}/>
        <Route path="/register" render={() => <Auth authType = "register"/>}/>
    </Routes>
</main>)

export default RouteViews
